// src/ui/i18n.ts
// Lightweight, dependency-free i18n for the UI chrome. Keyed dictionaries keep
// it readable and i18next-migratable: a new locale is one more object, and the
// t(key, params) call sites would survive a future library swap. The game LOG
// is intentionally NOT translated here (it is generated by the engine).
